name: Naming Is Hard
description:
Generates nice random names for new projects and modules.

If you would like to see support for a wizard you use please leave a review!

The plugin supports different name generation methods: Mythical Creatures, Fairy Tale Titles, Swedish Furniture, J.R.R. Tolkien Characters, Island Names.

Supported wizards: Gradle, Maven, Spring Initializr, Micronaut, Quarkus, MicroProfile, Selenium


Plugin icon made by Freepik, Option icons made by Smashicons from www.flaticon.com.
notes: Multiple name generation methods supported: Mythical Creatures, Fairy Tale Titles, Swedish Furniture, J.R.R. Tolkien Characters, Island Names.
